Algorithm name: GA-based optimisation [stochastic]
	Thread safety: none

Extra info:
	Generations: 1000
	Mutation probability pm: 0.5
	Crossover probability cm: 0.3
	Seed: None
	Log level: 1
	Selection for Crossover: Roulette wheel
	Left part Crossover: Position-based crossover for permutation encoding
	Middle part Crossover: Two-point crossover for binary encoding
	Right part Crossover: None
	Left part Mutation: Swap mutation for permutation encoding
	Middle part Mutation: Random select and reverse value
	Right part Mutation: Select half and change according to condition
	Generation Selection: mu + lambda selection to maintain the high quality of solutions
